<v-toolbar flat>
  <!-- dropdown menu -->
  <v-menu offset-y>
    <v-toolbar-side-icon slot="activator"></v-toolbar-side-icon>

    <v-list class="mt-3">
      <v-layout row wrap>
        <v-flex xs4 sm4 md4 v-for="link in links" :key="link.text" router :to="link.route">
          <v-list-tile>
            <v-list-tile-title>{{ link.text }}</v-list-tile-title>
          </v-list-tile>
        </v-flex>
      </v-layout>
    </v-list>
  </v-menu>
  <v-toolbar-items offset-y class="hidden-sm-and-down">
    <v-text-field
      solo
      class="styled-input mt-2"
      height="1"
      placeholder="Buscar"
      color="white"
      append-icon="search"
      v-model="search"
    ></v-text-field>
  </v-toolbar-items>
</v-toolbar>
